</emphasis>
: Total Length: 11.20, PL: 5.32, PW: 5.47, OL: 5.88, OW: 3.66, AW: 2.87. 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="77">Eyes</emphasis>
: AME: 0.25, ALE: 0.37, PME: 0.30, PLE: 0.42, AME-AME: 0.17, AME-ALE: 0.09, PME-PME: 0.25, PME-PLE: 0.37, AME-PME: 0.40, ALE-PLE: 0.37, clypeus AME: 1.11, clypeus ALE: 1.10. 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="77">Palp</emphasis>
